  • Method Details

    • setResource

      public void setResource(String name, Object data)
      Sets the worker-level data for the given name. This data can then be read by all components running on the same worker, i.e. tasks (spouts, bolts), task hooks and worker hooks.
      Parameters:
      name - name of the worker-level data to be set
      data - worker-level data
